title: Helene Fischer - The English Ones CD plus bonus (musicfromrizzo)
description:
Here's some truly great and enjoyable singing in the English language from
Germany's beauty queen and supreme song talent Ms. Helene Fischer

Helene Fischer - Don't ask.mp3
Helene Fischer - Everything I need.mp3
Helene Fischer - From here til forever.mp3
Helene Fischer - Goodbye my love.mp3
Helene Fischer - Heaven is here.mp3
Helene Fischer - I'll walk with you.mp3
Helene Fischer - Leave me.mp3
Helene Fischer - My heart belongs to you.mp3
Helene Fischer - Only dreamers.mp3
Helene Fischer - Sometimes love.mp3
Helene Fischer - Sweet surrender.mp3
Helene Fischer - Wake me up.mp3
Helene Fischer - You let me shine.mp3
Helene Fischer - You're my destination.mp3

Bonus - mini mp4 (26MB version only) of Helene Fischer sining the Power of Love
This singing was done around the time Helene also offered her very best DVD
performance of some gloriously supremely done renditions of The Russian Medley,
and this singing of The Power of Love (also done by Celine Dion previously) We do have these two song performances posted here for you in DivX at a nice
enough bitrate for many, however in addition we plan to post an H.264 6000k video bitrate version of these two song performances from that DVD (Mut Zum Gefühl-Live) (musicfromrizzo)(we also have the full DVD posted here in full DVD or 4000k MP4 video bitrate 448k AC3 audio version)

Please seed - with thanks indeed
Michael Rizzo Chessman
(musicfromrizzo)
